'''Kol Eyttyn''' was a [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] and [[Commander/Legends|commander]] in the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]]. He was the commander of the [[X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]] assigned to the ''[[Thurse]]''.

